  - {fileID: 1459832038}
  - {fileID: 967541559}
  - {fileID: 161959843}
  - {fileID: 1115163847}
  - {fileID: 448804823}
  objectiveLabels:
  - Independent auditor se district mandate aur state-expansion eligibility verify
    karein
  - Eight fictional seats ka comparable public-issue atlas lock karein
  - Eight-seat fictional candidate slate ko published ethics criteria se vet karein
  - Receipt-backed small-donor campaign fund aur conflict register audit karein
  - Eight-seat volunteer cohort ko lawful polling and safety protocol train karein
  - Shanti ke saath equal-time public candidate debate complete karein
  - Phased field campaign ya all-seat media blitz mein strategic decision lein
  - Threat report ko evidence-safe neutral public-safety channel se file karein
  - Eight seats ka polling logistics and accessibility dry-run pass karein
  - Eight-seat evidence-led convention aur objection session complete karein
  - Candidate, funding, consent and anti-hate compliance audit lock karein
  - Independent panel par computed eight-seat result aur state foothold dekhein
  milestoneSteps: 03000000070000000a000000
  milestoneTitles:
  - EIGHT-SEAT BASELINE LOCKED
  - CAMPAIGN STRATEGY ACTIVE
  - POLLING SYSTEM READY
  milestoneMessages:
  - District mandate, issue atlas and candidate slate verified. Ab clean funding,
    teams and debate ready karo.
  - Funding, training, debate and strategy complete. Safety evidence and polling
    operations next hain.
  - Safety response, polling dry-run and public convention complete. Final compliance
    result decide karega.
